Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MC大獎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其四  英雄來遲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是放學後茶會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為MC啊  你們看  麥克風測試的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.10,0:00:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有去卡卡地敲麥克風吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以為是這個省略呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.44,0:00:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麥克（Mic）卡卡（Concon）就叫MC
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有人說這是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「漫談  Comical」才叫MC
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.84,0:00:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有人說那也是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司儀（Master of Ceremonies）的略稱才叫MC啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master哦  Ceremonies的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種安定感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當之無愧的Master of Ceremonies
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.91,0:00:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MC大獎獲主出現了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:01:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這比賽根本沒什麼意義啊…

